signatureAbility.signatureDescription: Blockers with this ability reduce a pass rusher's chances of using a quick block shed move.
The most effective ball carriers prioritize maintaining possession over all else. When they enter the zone, no tackles made against them will result in a fumble.
Ballcarriers with this ability have more powerful stiff arm animations.
Some pass rushers intimidate quarterbacks with their sheer presence. When they enter the zone, they can apply significant pressure on quarterbacks even while engaged with blockers.
Defenders with this ability can apply pressure to the quarterback from a greater distance.
Defenders with this ability have faster power move animations during their pass rush.
Defenders with this ability are rarely faked out by ballcarrier moves (and cannot be faked out when user-controlled).

signatureAbility.signatureActivationDescription: Make consecutive passes for 5+ yards in air
signatureAbility.signatureDescription: Fearless quarterbacks are unintimidated by the pass rush. When they enter the zone, their passing accuracy is unaffected by defensive pressure.
Passers with this ability have perfect accuracy on all throws inside the numbers (except on high/low throws).
Passers with this ability can make all hot route and blocking adjustments twice as fast (excluding audibles).
Midway through the fourth quarter in close games, players with this ability can easily enter (and remain in) the Zone.
Receivers with this ability run sharper routes and catch more consistently while running in and out routes.
When Selfless players are making plays their teammates are motivated to perform better. When they enter the zone, all on field teammates enter the zone as well.
